{"title":"在天上作画——看“八一”飞行表演队表演有感","authors":["巩怀书"],"dates":[{"year":2003,"month":11,"day":11}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天上作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——看“八一”飞行表演队表演有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巩怀书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，飞行员——作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自如潇洒，气势宏大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画屏——天空"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整整一个天下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画笔——翅翼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天风云任挥洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画什么？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不画毕加索的白鸽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不画徐悲鸿的骏马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大写意——锦绣中华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横一笔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从东海朝阳画到昆仑晚霞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纵一笔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从白山黑水画到曾母暗沙"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上下画……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从九霄云外画到三峡大坝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一笔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱蘸的真情都无价"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一笔……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都画在五星红旗下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我，为什么这样画？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是我可爱的中华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山也精神，河也焕发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本来就是一首赞美诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是一幅壮丽的风景画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这块大地，我常牵挂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里有爸有妈还有“她”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这里是我温馨的家！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在天上作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"广阔天空尽情挥洒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出航，竖起一道警示线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巡逻，横插上利剑一把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"疯狂的强盗胆敢来侵犯"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"等着他的——这副十字架！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在天上作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"画幅战鹰打空靶"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"航炮、火箭齐发"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"火力猛，巧交叉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满天火树银花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国啊，放心吧"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严严实实扎紧了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝天上的铁篱笆！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在天上作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机群跃升，是一颗紧包的蕾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骤然散开，是朵盛开的莲花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"俯冲直下，飞下来利剑六把"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呼啦声解散，一口金钟倒挂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多么喜庆啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一束束鲜艳的花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"献给祖国现代化"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在天上作画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨云雾凝结成标题"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忠诚和激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浓缩为一句话："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞美祖国挺进的步伐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祝我的祖国兴旺发达！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":14,"page_end":14}